JavaScript -> Synchronus and Single Threaded
    (Default JS Behaviour)    Synchronus matlab ek code fir ek code aise execute hoga, by default ye Synchronus h.
    Single Threaded H .

Execution Context -> line by line, each operation waits for the last one to complete before executing 

    Blocking Code                   v/s     Non Blocking Code
    Block the Flow of Program               does not block the flow of code
    Read File Sync                          read file Async 
    (tum koi kaam mat kro, jabtak           (Apna kaam karo, m dusra kaam krta hu)
